  "detailed_description": "<h1>OUR DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/c79edd2220dab6dbf189f55e7ac14c5b.poster.avif?t=1724981444\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/c79edd2220dab6dbf189f55e7ac14c5b.webm?t=1724981444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/c79edd2220dab6dbf189f55e7ac14c5b.mp4?t=1724981444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAMEPLAY</h2>In Lying Souls, you experience a story in which you have to solve the mysterious circumstances of a long-ago incident in your family in first person. You will experience different parts of the story to piece together the truth.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE STORY</h2>It's been a while since the incident. Back then you were too young to understand. Now you start looking for clues and realize that there is a cruel secret behind it all, and haunted by the consequences of the incident, you do your best not to lose your mind.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/ce4969b502c1ed5ab877db2aec683c26.poster.avif?t=1724981444\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/ce4969b502c1ed5ab877db2aec683c26.webm?t=1724981444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/ce4969b502c1ed5ab877db2aec683c26.mp4?t=1724981444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAIN FEATURES</h2><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story / Decisions:</li></ul></strong> You will have to make a decision at some moment. There are smaller and bigger decisions. But whether you will find out everything, is questionable.<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Notes / Recordings:</li></ul></strong> You will come across a number of audio recordings and various writings and notes. They will help you put the story together.<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Random Events:</li></ul></strong> You will experience some random events from time to time. They are always part of the current story and gameplay when they happen.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/e2f69657848559ca40be6129fb0691d3.poster.avif?t=1724981444\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/e2f69657848559ca40be6129fb0691d3.webm?t=1724981444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/e2f69657848559ca40be6129fb0691d3.mp4?t=1724981444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/c79edd2220dab6dbf189f55e7ac14c5b.poster.avif?t=1724981444\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/c79edd2220dab6dbf189f55e7ac14c5b.webm?t=1724981444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/c79edd2220dab6dbf189f55e7ac14c5b.mp4?t=1724981444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAMEPLAY</h2>In Lying Souls, you experience a story in which you have to solve the mysterious circumstances of a long-ago incident in your family in first person. You will experience different parts of the story to piece together the truth.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE STORY</h2>It's been a while since the incident. Back then you were too young to understand. Now you start looking for clues and realize that there is a cruel secret behind it all, and haunted by the consequences of the incident, you do your best not to lose your mind.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/ce4969b502c1ed5ab877db2aec683c26.poster.avif?t=1724981444\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/ce4969b502c1ed5ab877db2aec683c26.webm?t=1724981444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/ce4969b502c1ed5ab877db2aec683c26.mp4?t=1724981444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAIN FEATURES</h2><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story / Decisions:</li></ul></strong> You will have to make a decision at some moment. There are smaller and bigger decisions. But whether you will find out everything, is questionable.<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Notes / Recordings:</li></ul></strong> You will come across a number of audio recordings and various writings and notes. They will help you put the story together.<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Random Events:</li></ul></strong> You will experience some random events from time to time. They are always part of the current story and gameplay when they happen.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/e2f69657848559ca40be6129fb0691d3.poster.avif?t=1724981444\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/e2f69657848559ca40be6129fb0691d3.webm?t=1724981444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/e2f69657848559ca40be6129fb0691d3.mp4?t=1724981444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
